&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Build Integrations:&lt;/strong&gt; Design and develop connections with 3rd party SaaS tools using APIs.&lt;/p&gt;
